        "category": "Divination_and_Omens",
        "entity_or_term": "التشاؤمُ بالعطاسِ, التيمُّن بالمقاسمْ",
        "notes": "This verse refers to the pre-Islamic practices of taking omens from sneezing (al-tashāʾum bi-l-ʿiṭās) and seeking good fortune from lots or shares (al-tayammun bi-l-maqāsim), both forms of divination."
      },
